source.en: Blaser, Magdalena "Myths of the Cofán people"

sentences.text: Tayopi tsu tisuyi canse fae tsandie pusheve mechoa.
Tsa tsandie biani tsampini jacamba fae pushesuma cachai.
Tsa pushesuta te quini'jin setsa'choni dyai.
Tsama cachaipa me'nde'visi in'jamba catsepa condasepa tise'ma in'jan qquen susi tsa tsandie'ja tseniñi ana.
Tsa'caen anamba fae'ngae can'jemba tsaoni ji.
Jipa ccase jaye tson'jensi se'pi'fa.
Se'pipa pushesunga antteye in'jan'fa.
Cuintsu pushepa jambe cañe.
Pusheve mechopa me'ndetsse tsampini ana jacan qquen in'jamba.
Tsa'caen in'jamba fae tsandie tise'ma iñajampañamba su:
¿Queta ti qui ña onque'ngemajan pusheya'mbi?
- Tsonsi tsa chu'a tsandie'ja su:
- Me'in in'jambi gi.
Pusheya'mbi gi, chi'ga gi.
- Ñanda gi pushepa, ña pushema gi an'bian.
- ¿Ma'caen gi ccoan'giveja pusheya?
- ¿Tsa'caenda micomba tsu tise'ja quei'ccu jipa can'jembi?
- Ñoa'me gi su: ña pusheta tsu tsampini canse'su.
- Ñoa'mendi qui su: tsa'caen da in'gaja ingi atteye.
Tsa'caen susi pañamba cui'ccuma cui'je ccusipa sombopa ja tise pushema inga'su.
Japa tisei'ccu fae'ngae tise pushema i.
Cca'i caña'jen'ni musin ipa can'niamba fae'ngae fae'tti dyai'fa.
Tsa'caen ipa tsangae canqqueni canseye i.
Tsomba ba've canse'fa.
Tsa'caen can'jen'ni tsa canqque'su a'indeccuja bo'fa tsetse'pama cui'ye ashaen'fa.
Cui'ye ashaemba ccusipa ccoshai'ccu ccoshapa tungru, tungru, tungru tungru qquen avujatsse buira'je'fa.
Buira'je cosepa anambe'yi a'taji'fa.
Tsetse'pama injan'tsse cu'i'fa oan'oan pushesu cui'qquian'choma.
Tsa cui'ccuja sefambi, tise'pa sefaenjin'faninda ccase omba'je.
Tise tsa'nduja cui'ccu sefa'ninda a'i atte'fasa'ne tise pushema mandaje cuintsu nasipaccuni jaye.
Nasipaccuni japa coyema qqueshopa ija cui'ccuve tsonjan qquen manda'je.
Tsa pushesuja coyeccuni japa oan'oame di'shapa tsene a'tutsse tsaoni jipa ettinga can'nimba apinga can'ni ppipa cui'ccuve tson'jen.
Tsa'caen tson'supa tise tsa'ndu mandasi coyeccuni japa di'shapa tayo tise cuiccu apinga can'ni ppipa cuiqquian'jen.
Tsanga tise antian chu'aja tise quindyama iñajampañamba, tayo tise cui'ccuma sefaemba coyeve ja qquen in'jamba apinga japa fetta can.
Tsa'cae camba atte fae oan'oan cui'ccuni ttontton'baen ppi'choma.
Tsomba ñoa'me oan'oan qquen in'jamba su: Oan'oancco'o tsu cui'ccunga can'ni ppipa amu'ndetsse ttonttomboen'jengi.
Qquen supa tsa apima ccaccuni angapa fiña cati oan'oani'ccu fae'ngae.
Tsa'caen tsomba apima toe'ttinga cashiccutsian.
Tsa'caen tson ccutsian'chonga tise she'sheja coyema re'ri'ccoe qque'sho'choma i.
Tsama attejangipa su: Oan'oancco'o tsu cuiccu apini amu'ndetsse ttonttomboen ppi'ya.
Queta qui ña quindyamajan amu'ndetsse cuiña'jen'ña.
Tsa'caen qque gi in'jaña qquen tsa pushesuja su.
Tsa cuiccucho'anjan catiya'cho tsu.
Tsa'ma tise tsa'ndumbe antianjan su: Tayo gi pa'cho'an oan'oani'ccu fae'ngae fiñacatipa cashi ccutsian'ña.
Tsonsi unjan, qquen supa coyema anga'choma otaemba saparonga cupaen ccutsian.
Tsa pushesu cuiccu apini dyai'choja a'i attesi iyicca'ye.
Tsa'caen iyicca'yepa ccui'choma tise tsa'nduja atesumbi'pa anañe ccuipa tise pushei'ccu ccuipa iñajan.
Tsa'caen iñajamba tson'jensi ti'tsse tsonjan, ti'tsse tsonjan qquen su'je tsa pushesuja.
Tsa'caen su'je oan'oame di'shapa tise cundyi'je'fama tsai indi.
Tsa'caen tsai indipa etti'ye somboin japa tsa'ndumbema qquitssa biañamba quinijin setsaccunga, bombo setsanga angapa shonquendipa naiqui tsutoni angapa chango'su quini'cconga fi'ndipa tseni dyainga.
Tsomba ño'fapa tsa pushesuja tsangae nepi.
Tsa'caen tsonsi tsa tsandieja un, un, qquen attuse'je.
Tsonsi japa attepa su'fa: ¿Majan tsu quemajan jova'caen jan tson?
Tsonsi su: Tsa oan'oan pushesu tsu ñama qquen tsomba jasi gi paye tson'jen.
Qquen tise tsa'nduja afa ccui.
Tsa'caen tsomba jasi tise mamajan attepa in'namba apiccuma isupa japa vanamba pa'cco tise du'shu ttopa'fama tai apiccunga.
Tsomba ipa na'sui'ccu pporotsse ccutsian.
Tsa'caen dasi coragandeccuja inza'pa, yajema otaemba cu'ipa se'jema osha'fambi ma'caen tise cundyi'je'choma chipiriañe.
Tsa'caen oshambi'pa tssararacco cocoyama ttu'se'fa, cuintsu jipa se'jeye.
Tsomba ma'ttinga tssararacco jiya'choma atesupa jipa conda'fa ma'caen tsoña'choma.
Tsomba ccani tsaoñasiamba tseni angapa ccuiña'fa.
Tsa'caen ccuiña'fasi ccuipa in'namba quia'me fundo'je.
Fundo'jesi cajeni'su a'indeccuja pañamba tiseningae" tro, tro, tro, qquen tise'paningae shavongae jiña'fa.
Tsonsi su'fa: ¿Majan tsu jiña?
Qquen supa camba tsu atte'fa: Tsai'mbi'tssi singo a'ima.
Shiñoi'ccu camba'juma tivema te'vapa jiña'fa'choma.
Ccoanifae pushesu, ccoa'ngi tsandie tsu jiña'fa.
Tise'paja napoa'can'fa, tsandiendeccuja camisapa'fa.
Toya'caen tsu iña'fa seje'suma.
Tsendeccu jipa ccattufa'fa tise ccui'tti pporotsse.
Seje'suja sombopa cca'indeccuma su:
Que'ija va'tti ronda'je'faja.
Tsomba paji'sunga catsepa su:
¿Micomba qui paye tson'jen?
Qquen dapa gi paye tson'jen.
Atesu gi asi'ttaembe canjan, ronda'jeja ingi o'te añe.
Amba tteppupa gi jiya quema cañe.
Qquen supa japa zenzecco, bavoroma añe isupa faesu ccuivoma ccoma randeve tson'fa toya'caen bavoromajan totoa ccomame tsomba tsa'iccu an'fa.
Tsa'caen tsomba an ananimba tse'ija ccumbama isupa chhi'chhi'fa.
Tsomba tsa'ccuma fiñamba tssutssiamba cu'i'fa.
Cu'ipa ccusipa setta'fa.
Tsa setta'choja paji'sumbe cundyi'je'fama tsu cashiqquia'caen pa'cco amundetssia'ma giyaen.
Tsa'caen tsomba tise cundyi'je'fama isupa mandyi, mandyi zuruchoen'fa.
Zuruchoemba seje'suja su: Re'ri'cco tsu shaca.
Tsa'caen supa ccase mandyi, mandyipa paji'suma iñajampañamba su:
¿Minga qui?
Ñotssi gi re'ri'cho'cco tsu.
Tayo qui ñotsse da.
Asi'ttaembe opatsse canjan, ñoa'me qui ccushaya.
Qquen supa ja'fasi tssararacco cocoyandeccu'qque japa camba atte'fa, tayo ñotsse da'choma.
Tsomba sejesundeccuja tise'pa shavongae ja'fa.
Tsonsi ccushapa canseepa tsa tsandie'ja pa.
